1	//! Byte-parity tests: render functions vs. captured oracle response bodies.
2	//!
3	//! Fixtures under `tests/fixtures/` are captured program OUTPUT (allowed
4	//! observation material per the clean-room protocol), extracted verbatim from
5	//! the crawl manifests. Each test feeds the observed input slots into a render
6	//! function and asserts the produced bytes equal the captured response.
