156	// Solved proof tree (west pane after autoprove), reproduced from the observed
157	// proof-line model. The lemma declarations, proof-method HTML and case names
158	// are prover fragments (loaded from fixtures); every wrapper — the header
159	// status span, indentation, anchors, keyword spans, by-prefix, remove-step
160	// anchor, case/next/qed markup, href construction and blank-line spacing — is
161	// generated by the crate and asserted byte-for-byte against the capture.
